				<p id="ghGen307">
					<sent id="ghGen308" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen308">1. <strong>What is the smallest Great ape?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen309">
					<sent id="ghGen310" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen310"> a. orangutan</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen311">
					<sent id="ghGen312" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen312"> b. chimpanzee</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen313">
					<sent id="ghGen314" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen314"> c. gorilla</sent>
				</p>


				<p id="ghGen315">
					<sent id="ghGen316" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen316">2. <strong>Great apes do not have what?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen317">
					<sent id="ghGen318" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen318"> a. a tail</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen319">
					<sent id="ghGen320" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen320"> b. hands</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen321">
					<sent id="ghGen322" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen322"> c. ears</sent>
				</p>


				<p id="ghGen323">
					<sent id="ghGen324" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen324">3. <strong>Chimpanzees have a lot in common with?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen325">
					<sent id="ghGen326" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen326"> a. fish</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen327">
					<sent id="ghGen328" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen328"> b. humans</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen329">
					<sent id="ghGen330" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen330"> c. horses</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen331">
					<sent id="ghGen332" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen332">4. <strong> Chimpanzees do not grow hair on what part of their body?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen333">
					<sent id="ghGen334" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen334"> a. arms</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen335">
					<sent id="ghGen336" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen336"> b. stomach</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen337">
					<sent id="ghGen338" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen338"> c. face</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen339">
					<sent id="ghGen340" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen340">5. <strong>Chimpanzees grow to be how tall?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen341">
					<sent id="ghGen342" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen342"> a. four feet</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen343">
					<sent id="ghGen344" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen344"> b. two feet</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen345">
					<sent id="ghGen346" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen346"> c. six feet</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen347">
					<sent id="ghGen348" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen348">6. <strong> Where do chimpanzees spend most of their time?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen349">
					<sent id="ghGen350" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen350"> a. in the water</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen351">
