				</p>
				<p id="ghGen353">
					<sent id="ghGen354" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen354"> c. on the ground</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen355">
					<sent id="ghGen356" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen356">7. <strong>Why do chimpanzees groom each other?</strong></sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen357">
					<sent id="ghGen358" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen358"> a. to keep clean</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen359">
					<sent id="ghGen360" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen360"> b. to keep calm</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen361">
					<sent id="ghGen362" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen362"> c. both a and b</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen363">
					<sent id="ghGen364" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen364">8. <strong>What do chimpanzees use as tools?</strong></sent>
				</p>
