					<sent id="ghGen368" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen368"> b. pots and pans</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen369">
					<sent id="ghGen370" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen370"> c. sticks and rocks</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen371">
					<sent id="ghGen372" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen372">9. <strong>Who is the leader in a chimpanzee community?</strong></sent>
				</p>
