					<sent id="ghGen374" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen374"> a. a male </sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen375">
					<sent id="ghGen376" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen376"> b. a female</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen377">
					<sent id="ghGen378" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen378"> c. a baby</sent>
				</p>
				<p id="ghGen379">
					<sent id="ghGen380" smilref="Chimpanzees.smil#ghGen380"> 10. <strong>Where did Jane Goodall study chimpanzees?</strong></sent>
				</p>
